    "is_bundle": false,
    "feature_bullets": [
      "\u301011 Stages Filtration\u3011PUREPLUS 11-stage bathtub water filter is made of high quality ABS material, advanced filtration system effectively eliminates pollutants. It effectively removes impurities, reduces chlorine, and enriches the water with essential minerals. It provides a clean, refreshing bathing experience and is beneficial for your skin and hair.",
      "\u3010Improve Water Quality\u3011PUREPLUS bathtub filter uses advanced technology and contains KDF 55, alkaline ceramic balls, and calcium sulfite to remove 99% of harmful impurities, including chlorine, heavy metals, taste & odor, fluoride, rust, and sediment. Enriched with Vitamin C balls, mineralizing balls, tourmaline, anion balls and infrared balls to provide Vitamin C and beneficial minerals for a pure bathing experience all year round.",
      "\u3010Easy Installation\u3011No additional tools are required to install our bath filter for tub, it easily mounts to all standard bathtub. Includes standard flexible handle and velcro to suit various designs, making installation effortless and quick.With portable design, it is slao an ideal choice for bathing in RVs, hotels, etc. Enjoy clean, pure water and maintain your skincare routine no matter where you go.",
      "\u3010Long-Lasting Performance\u3011PUREPLUS bathtub water filters provide up to 2500 gallons of filtration, making them a long-lasting, cost-effective solution that provides lasting protection and effectively purifies water at any water temperature, ensuring a pristine bathing experience year-round.Replacing your filter about every 6 months depending on usage and water quality.",
      "\u3010High Water Flow Capacity\u3011Our filter is the perfect choice for quickly and effectively filtering large volumes of water. Our innovative design ensures that even with its extensive filtration process, water flow remains consistent, providing you with a spa-like shower experience. You can enjoy the benefits of purified and enriched water without compromising on water pressure."
    ],
    "feature_bullets_count": 5,
    "feature_bullets_flat": "\u3010High Water Flow Capacity\u3011Our filter is the perfect choice for quickly and effectively filtering large volumes of water. Our innovative design ensures that even with its extensive filtration process, water flow remains consistent, providing you with a spa-like shower experience. You can enjoy the benefits of purified and enriched water without compromising on water pressure. \u3010Long-Lasting Performance\u3011PUREPLUS bathtub water filters provide up to 2500 gallons of filtration, making them a long-lasting, cost-effective solution that provides lasting protection and effectively purifies water at any water temperature, ensuring a pristine bathing experience year-round.Replacing your filter about every 6 months depending on usage and water quality. \u3010Easy Installation\u3011No additional tools are required to install our bath filter for tub, it easily mounts to all standard bathtub. Includes standard flexible handle and velcro to suit various designs, making installation effortless and quick.With portable design, it is slao an ideal choice for bathing in RVs, hotels, etc. Enjoy clean, pure water and maintain your skincare routine no matter where you go. \u3010Improve Water Quality\u3011PUREPLUS bathtub filter uses advanced technology and contains KDF 55, alkaline ceramic balls, and calcium sulfite to remove 99% of harmful impurities, including chlorine, heavy metals, taste & odor, fluoride, rust, and sediment. Enriched with Vitamin C balls, mineralizing balls, tourmaline, anion balls and infrared balls to provide Vitamin C and beneficial minerals for a pure bathing experience all year round. \u301011 Stages Filtration\u3011PUREPLUS 11-stage bathtub water filter is made of high quality ABS material, advanced filtration system effectively eliminates pollutants. It effectively removes impurities, reduces chlorine, and enriches the water with essential minerals. It provides a clean, refreshing bathing experience and is beneficial for your skin and hair.",
